extend layout

block content

  section#content
    include content_header.jade
    // Section
    section.section.full-width-bg.gray-bg
      .row
        .col-lg-12.col-md-12.col-sm-12
          // Single Blog Post
          .blog-post-single.fullwidth-post
            .post-side-meta.animate-onscroll
              .date(style='padding-Top:0')
                span.day 17
                span.month DEC
              .post-comments
                a(href='blog-single-sidebar.html#comments')
                  i.icons.icon-chat-empty
                  |  13
            h1(style='margin-Top:20px') #{title}
            .post-meta.animate-onscroll
              span
                | by 
                a(href='#') admin
              span
                | in 
                a(href='#') Politics
                | , 
                a(href='#') Videos
            .post-content
              p.animate-onscroll.no-margin-bottom
                | #{detail}
                br
                | Vivamus eget nibh. Etiam cursus leo vel metus. Nulla facilisi. Aenean nec eros. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Suspendisse sollicitudin velit sed leo. Ut pharetra augue nec augue. Nam elit agna,endrerit sit amet, tincidunt ac, viverra sed, nulla. Donec porta diam eu massa. Quisque diam lorem, interdum vitae,dapibus ac, scelerisque vitae, pede. Donec eget tellus non erat lacinia fermentum. Donec in velit vel ipsum auctor pulvinar. Vestibulum iaculis lacinia est. Proin dictum elementum velit.
              
            // Post Meta Track
            .post-meta-track.animate-onscroll
              table.project-details
                tr
                  td.share-media
                    ul.social-share
                      li Share this:
                      li.facebook
                        a.tooltip-ontop(href='#', title='Facebook')
                          i.icons.icon-facebook
                      li.twitter
                        a.tooltip-ontop(href='#', title='Twitter')
                          i.icons.icon-twitter
                      li.google
                        a.tooltip-ontop(href='#', title='Google Plus')
                          i.icons.icon-gplus
                      li.pinterest
                        a.tooltip-ontop(href='#', title='Pinterest')
                          i.icons.icon-pinterest-3
                      li.email
                        a.tooltip-ontop(href='#', title='Email')
                          i.icons.icon-mail
                  td.tags
                    | Tags: 
                    a(href='#') meeting
                    | , 
                    a(href='#') politics
                    | , 
                    a(href='#') photos
